'''2015年薩拉熱窩槍擊案'''，是指2015年11月一宗發生在[[波斯尼亞|波斯尼亞]]首都[[薩拉熱窩|薩拉熱窩]]、造成多人死傷的[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]][[槍擊|槍擊]]事件，由信奉[[賽萊菲|賽萊菲]]運動的{{link-en|伊斯蘭極端主義|Islamic extremism}}份子所為。

== 背景 ==
波斯尼亞的[[基督徒|基督徒]]和[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]各佔該國人口的約45%，而截至2015年9月，最少有94名波斯尼亞公民到敘利亞參與[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]的[[吉哈德|聖戰]]組織<ref name=background>{{cite news|author1=Umberto Bacchi|title=Bosnia: Gunman kills two soldiers and blows himself up in Sarajevo 'terror' attack|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/bosnia-gunman-kills-two-soldiers-blows-himself-sarajevo-terror-attack-1529474|accessdate=2015-12-01|agency=IBTimes|date=2015-11-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120181646/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/bosnia-gunman-kills-two-soldiers-blows-himself-sarajevo-terror-attack-1529474|archivedate=2015-11-20|deadurl=no}}</ref>。是次襲擊的主兇埃內斯·奧梅拉吉克是一名[[賽萊菲|賽萊菲]]運動（極端保守伊斯蘭運動）信徒<ref name=process>{{cite news|title=Sarajevo gunman commits suicide after killing two soldiers|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/19/us-bosnia-attacks-idUSKCN0T735520151119|accessdate=2015-12-01|agency=REUTERS|date=2015-11-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151119231608/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/11/19/us-bosnia-attacks-idUSKCN0T735520151119|archivedate=2015-11-19|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

而自從較早前在[[巴黎|巴黎]]發生的[[2015年11月巴黎襲擊事件|恐怖襲擊事件]]後，[[歐洲|歐洲]]各國都已經加強戒備<ref>{{cite news|author1=Rodolfo Toe|title=Sarajevo Gunman's Identity and Suicide Confirmed|url=http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnian-police-confirms-the-identity-of-the-attacker-said-he-committed-suicide-11-19-2015|accessdate=2015-12-01|agency=Balkan Insight|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124033028/http://www.balkaninsight.com/en/article/bosnian-police-confirms-the-identity-of-the-attacker-said-he-committed-suicide-11-19-2015|archivedate=2015-11-24|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

== 經過 ==
